race.comment: ZAVABOOM (2) has been in good form, scoring three back at this track then placing twice in a row, most recently finishing second over 1200m at this track. Finds a tougher race but another big run will not surprise. HEAVENLY LEGEND (1) scored at this circuit last time out with one length in reserve at the end of 1000m. Has started three times at this course and distance and is yet to miss the placings. Best form puts him right in this. DANCE WIZZARD (3) made progress last time out, finishing 4 lengths from the winner in third at the end of 1200m here. Meets some better types this time but he has the talent to test this line-up. TORONADO ROUGE (4) missed the placings two runs back then improved last start but found a couple better over 1400m at Richmond Qld. Finds a suitable race and can find the winner's circle.
